vulnerability.name: USN-6751-1
vulnerability.description: It was discovered that Zabbix incorrectly handled input data in the discovery and graphs pages. A remote authenticated attacker could possibly use this issue to perform reflected cross-site scripting (XSS) attacks. (CVE-2022-35229, CVE-2022-35230)

statements.status_notes: Zabbix could allow reflected cross-site scripting (XSS) attacks. Available with Ubuntu Pro.
